name: B-Total
description:
B Vitamins are factors in providing energy by converting carbohydrates into glucose.

This product has a delicious fruit flavor and will last you 30-days.

Take one full dropper (1 cc) in the morning as a vitamin supplement, or before physical activity for a natural burst of energy.

Supplement Facts:
Vitamin B12 - 1,000 mcg
Vitamin B2 - 1.7 mg
Vitamin B3 - 20 mg
Vitamin B6 - 2 mg
Vitamin B5 - 30 mg
Folic Acid - 400 mcg

For adults and children ages 12 and over.

name: Raspberry Ketone
description:
Raspberry Ketone is a healthy way to lose weight.  It burns fat, shrinks fat cells, curbs appetite, and speeds metabolism through the ingredients of raspberry ketones and garcinia cambogia.  Take 1 ml twice daily.

Ingredients:
Proprietary Raspberry Blend- Raspberry ketone, acai fruit, grapefruit extract, apple cider vinegar extract, African mango extract, HCA Garcinia Cambogia, caffeine

Supplement Facts:
Calories- 1.8 
Total Fat- 0 g
Total Protein- 0 g
Total Carbs- 0.15 g
Sugars- 0 g
